    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>\"I may have lost the power granted by youth, but I have gained wisdom granted by age\"</em></p><h5 id=\"prerequisites\">Prerequisites</h5><p>Be older than 50.</p><h5 id=\"benefit\">Benefit</h5><p>You start with 3 extra jutsu up to D-Rank that are treated as being learned with downtime. You also gain an additional background.</p><h5 id=\"negative\">Negative</h5><p>Your old age intensives the stress of combat. You take 1d8 Hp and Cp damage at the beginning of each of your turns after 3 rounds of combat has transpired.</p>",
